## Custom Libraries

| Library | What It Does |
|---------|-------------|
| **BP_mobile_util** | WebSocket client — connect, reconnect, topic register, publish. |
| **WIFI32_util** | WiFi connect, optional connection to NTP server to sync ESP32 Clock with world time. |
| **SD32_util** | CSV logging — open/flush/close, file naming, directory management. |
| **syncTime_util** | A helper library to deal with sub-second timestamps from a 1 s RTC tick: records a `millis()` sync point and interpolates ms elapsed; recalibrates when drift exceeds 1 s. |
| **CAN32_util** | Thin wrapper around ESP32 TWAI driver with debug helpers. |
| **DS3231_util** | DS3231 RTC read/set, format to Unix timestamp . |
| **ams_data_util** | `BMUdata`/`AMSdata`/`OBCdata` structs and CAN frame parser for BMU messages. [Details](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/12pS13Plre9t67ogZUqtdaa3BjL8dEgXgRLJaQJvscLw/edit?usp=sharing)|

